<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>ج ل خ<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span><span class="c4">[١٢٠٢ - ج ل خ]</span><a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>جلَّخَ يجلِّخ، تجليخًا، فهو مُجلِّخ، والمفعول مُجلَّخ<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span><span class="c5">• جلَّخ الشَّيءَ:</span> جَلَخه، قشَّره.<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span><span class="c5">• جلَّخ السِّكِّينَ:</span> جلَخ؛ صقلها، سنَّها، شحذها.<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>